  "title": "Inviting Light Norwegian Kabanos Sausage Toast",
  "description": "A cozy and light Norwegian dish featuring kabanos sausages and toast, perfect for a flexitarian snack. It combines the savory flavors of sausage with the comfort of toasted bread.",
