  "instructions": [
    "Preheat a non-stick skillet over medium heat.",
    "Butter each slice of bread on one side.",
    "Place the bread slices butter side down in the skillet and toast until golden brown.",
    "Flip the bread slices over and top each with a slice of kabanos sausage.",
    "Spread a layer of mayonnaise on top of the sausage.",
    "Add a dollop of dijon mustard on top of the mayonnaise.",
    "Sprinkle chopped parsley over the mustard.",
    "Season with salt and pepper to taste.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy."
